AR Laundromat, Atlantic City

About Us

Welcome to AR Laundromat, your one-stop-shop for all your laundry needs in Atlantic City. We provide a range of services to make laundry day as convenient and hassle-free as possible. Our facility features top-of-the-line washers and dryers, comfortable seating, free Wi-Fi, and a friendly and knowledgeable staff ready to assist you. We offer competitive pricing and our flexible hours ensure that you can do your laundry at a time that suits your schedule. Come visit us today and see why we're the best laundromat in Atlantic City.

Our Services

Drop off & Pick Up

AR Laundromat offers a convenient drop off and pick up laundry service in Atlantic City. With our drop off service, customers can simply bring in their laundry and let us take care of the rest. We will wash, dry, and fold your laundry to your specifications and have it ready for pick up at your convenience. Our pick up service is just as easy - simply schedule a time for us to pick up your laundry and we'll take care of it from there. With our reliable and efficient service, you can trust that your laundry will be in good hands with AR Laundromat.

Pick Up & Delivery

At AR Laundromat, we understand that your time is valuable, and that's why we offer a convenient pick up and delivery laundry service in Atlantic City. Our team will come to your location and pick up your laundry, then transport it to our facility for professional cleaning. Once your laundry is ready, we'll deliver it back to you at a time and location that suits you. With our pick up and delivery service, you'll save time and hassle, and you can trust that your laundry is in good hands with our experienced team. Contact us today to schedule your pick up and delivery service and experience the convenience of professional laundry cleaning.
